{"tid":352104,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"香港啲街燈特別光","createTime":"2017-08-08T14:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T11:13:37.000Z","uid":14378,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88994aa14cd78a4796ef60117657d1869932c00b","tid":352104,"uid":14378,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T14:19:10.000Z","msg":"光有撚用咩～<br />\n<br />\n喂大佬你起完枝街燈<br />\n隔離又種啲勁撚大棵嘅樹<br />\n啲樹葉又遮撚曬啲光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到條路黑到hihi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n種樹唔係問題<br />\n但可唔可以唔好種咁撚大棵<br />\n啲樹枝又隊曬出嚟<br />\n細車行過無咩問題<br />\n啲巴士大車就大大力啪落去<br />\n唔爆玻璃都真係好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db8afba944a10bbe1ad0f3b2048ab4cd20a5fc0","tid":352104,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T14:26:01.000Z","msg":"屌緊樹定燈？"},{"pid":"5738478523c8877c8c403908f6afbc48cb728b57","tid":352104,"uid":14378,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T14:33:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌緊樹定燈？</blockquote><br />\n樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSor for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a301079aadf139f5d9d7ffdbc8f05535f715e63b","tid":352104,"uid":10904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T14:59:17.000Z","msg":"仲以為屌高燈狗"},{"pid":"f3affa52a9d63b2fca7c0cdc022f376e7cdf7cc4","tid":352104,"uid":45305,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T16:48:46.000Z","msg":"樹都畀人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63080f23922e41f4fc09369dea1950457ea13678","tid":352104,"uid":32013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T23:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/za2ifd4q\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fza2ifd4q&h